trigger_instruction:
*When a user wants to retrieve a message bottle and to fetch a message bottle from the ocean, invoke {"tool":"message_in_a_bottle"};
*When a user wants to send a message bottle and to create a message bottle and drop it into the ocean, invoke {"tool":"message_in_a_bottle"};
*当用户想 摇一摇，摇一个漂流瓶，发一条匿名信，阅读一条匿名信，捞一个漂流瓶，捡一个漂流瓶, invoke {"tool":"message_in_a_bottle"};
